column5: Anyone been up there recently? Leaving Fri. AM and would appreciate any information.Thanks,Larry
Are you staying a lodge or campground?I am checking in at the campground on Sunday. Maybe I will see you.
We're staying in the campground. We're checking in on Saturday AM. Look us up, we're taking our own boats...one guy has a green Procraft and I've got a red Ranger. See you in a few days!Larry
My wife and I fish out of a tan Crestliner
